Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.99,0:04:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能继续往前走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.37,0:04:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部队强行突击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:05:02.58,Warning,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be1\blur3}翻译 洛艾妖 十八 斑马线 校译 洛艾妖 时间 仓鼠  后期 风
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.64,0:05:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点离开那里 小雪！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人攻过来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.68,0:05:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕获目标
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交涉决裂了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙… 居然连这个都有！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来须警官应该马上就会到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.03,0:05:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来须警官…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.78,0:05:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来须警官来了的话我会被杀掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课长！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人质在413室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想办法把人给救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是认真的吗 没得到上级的许可就强行突破
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西岛！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回警署去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.61,0:05:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课…课长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.39,0:06:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.91,0:06:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不逃掉的话会被杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.41,0:06:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来不及了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.66,0:06:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妻！ 休想得逞！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪辉将成为我的人质
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪 快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪辉！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的人质了 雪辉！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准动！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你敢动我就杀了他！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你敢动我就引爆它！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了 我妻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然我就炸飞一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.44,0:07:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5分后引爆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这多少能起点障眼法的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不认为这样就能回避得了DEAD END
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只能逃一步算一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.82,0:07:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 交易是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妻 我会放了雪辉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但与此相对的 你也要扔掉那个危险物品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.73,0:07:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先放
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下吧 雪辉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.16,0:08:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的哦 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小雪给了我这个本来就已经死掉的人未来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来当你未来的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.19,0:08:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我们长大了再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.29,0:08:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么还不快点长大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成大人的话……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.92,0:08:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点变成大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.05,0:08:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天野君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.78,0:08:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪是我活下去的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.62,0:08:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过如果连这个也无法实现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.94,0:08:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少让我为了小雪而死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.44,0:09:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算死了 我也会继续追着小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妻！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.62,0:09:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙就在这里和我一起去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 由乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和由乃一起去看星星…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.97,0:09:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨流美弥音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.39,0:09:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么又是你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.07,0:09:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于抓到你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.05,0:09:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪辉那家伙用了那个了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.33,0:10:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28\3c&HA74856&}命运的枷锁又将两个人联系到了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:09:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚有光…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.98,0:10:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是闪光弹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有些晃眼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实弹给他的话有点过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.59,0:10:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.43,0:10:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这还是晃眼而已么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 刚刚爆炸的是在四楼 是我安装的炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙没死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏遇到你 我想到了避开这个DEAD END的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.76,0:10:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.73,0:10:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来须警官
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也真是走狗屎运啊 雪辉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得在其他警察赶来之前 把你们杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话一切问题就解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的 雪辉 你是不会开枪的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想再开一次枪？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次可是对着我妻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把枪扔了 不然我就切掉我妻的头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒过来了么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我老实点 如果你自己挂了可就什么都捞不着了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.60,0:12:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4th
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你准备怎么做 雪辉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开枪的话 万一失手由乃就没命了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.73,0:12:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说都会有命中由乃的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看未来日记…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}子弹射中由乃 由乃中弹身亡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射中由乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话不就不能开枪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\frz46.408\c&H687A4C&\3c&HEBEFE3&\move(430,347,430,74)\shad0}小雪开枪了。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs26\c&H687A4C&\3c&HEBEFE3&\frz45.055\move(552,397,552,125)}小雪开枪把我打死了。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs26\c&H687A4C&\3c&HEBEFE3&\frz45.428\move(670,404,664,142)}天野雪辉将2ND射杀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开枪的话会击中由乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日记上写着不好的事情吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸色铁青呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是扔下枪的话 我们也会被杀死的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.79,0:12:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么做…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.44,0:12:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开枪吧 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.09,0:12:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被小雪射死也没关系哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能为小雪而死的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是说谎 小雪也曾说过我们是恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.87,0:13:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是假装也陪我参加了结婚仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.64,0:13:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经很幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.84,0:13:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住嘴 我妻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么鬼幸福 我才没闲工夫陪你们玩恋爱游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要随身带着这样的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃不想要变得更加幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是个超级跟踪狂 追着我有一年了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.48,0:13:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是想成为新娘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.83,0:13:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是没办法实现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.54,0:13:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有小雪一个人也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！别说什么没办法实现啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会给由乃幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.85,0:13:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人一起回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算由乃放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.64,0:14:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会放弃的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别逞强了 雪辉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.52,0:14:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妻会变成怎样都无所谓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.17,0:14:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…喜欢由乃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.34,0:14:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么能死！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来须警察 够了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:14:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为神的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成为神的话… 我就要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.43,0:15:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了 课长！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子赶上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.25,0:15:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西岛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.27,0:15:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月岛狩人事件还有栽赃雪辉一行人的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨流美弥音已经全部都交代了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算相信恐怖分子吗 西岛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.87,0:15:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你做个交易
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交易？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从一开始就没有攻击你的意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.59,0:15:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察的情报我也会继续泄露给你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很方便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放下武器吧 课长 我要逮捕你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮捕？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.10,0:15:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经不是警察了 只是个犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:16:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有调查权限的你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.95,0:16:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经无法预知搜查日记了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.78,0:16:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的未来日记被封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(434,164)\frz5.667\shad0\c&H92A342&\3c&HFFFFFF&}无警察情报。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\frz5.667\shad0\c&H92A342&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(412,270)}被雨流美弥音的枪所射杀。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.70,0:16:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老婆和孩子怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸前勉强救出了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人都没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9th
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这是我任性的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.00,0:16:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你能再次与我结盟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.79,0:16:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代价就是我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.55,0:16:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来须警官！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.07,0:16:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我儿子就拜托你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.76,0:16:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.52,0:16:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了啊 雪辉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不觉得这是道歉就能解决的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.94,0:17:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪辉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}6/13 20:10 子弹射中由乃 由乃中弹身亡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}6/13 20:11 4th射中我 我死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}6/13 20:11 避免DEAD END
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.72,0:17:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后 整件事情的处理就拜托给了西岛警官
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然我和由乃也被严厉地追究了责任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.17,0:17:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据来须先生所留下的“真相”资料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.17,0:17:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大部分的误解被解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.65,0:17:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知他是否已经预知到了这个结局
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经不得而知
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}樱见事件！ 在职警官所引发的不详时间！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.14,0:17:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来须警官的事件在世间引起了轰动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.26,0:17:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是却没有报道我们的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之后 9th好像也逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.63,0:17:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 都这个时间了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.22,0:17:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一可喜可贺的是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.95,0:17:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我打中的警察保住了性命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:17:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这之后要怎么办呢 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我想先到爸爸那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.79,0:18:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借望远镜用用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后登上高地…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.31,0:18:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果人生有最完美的happy end的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计就是像今天这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.83,0:18:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃你也太夸张了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的哦 我真想让这个瞬间变成永远 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.53,0:18:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻也稍稍熟练些了嘛 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别取笑我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您拨打的电话暂时无法接通
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:18:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.45,0:19:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联系不上爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.96,0:19:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电车来了哦 我们跑过去吧 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啦 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪辉君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有点时间 我去下洗手间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便买点饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.84,0:19:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\c&H687A4C&\3c&HEBEFE3&\shad0\frz4.293\move(781,256,777,30)}最好远离我妻。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.84,0:19:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\c&H687A4C&\3c&HEBEFE3&\shad0\frz2.661\move(349,335,346,111)}为了调查案情，警察正在搜寻她，但是她现下落不明。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋濑…或
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.84,0:19:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\c&H687A4C&\3c&HEBEFE3&\shad0\frz3.203\move(672,427,672,310)}一定要多加小心。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么 这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.37,0:19:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了啊 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.32,0:19:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪 还你手机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才好像有短信来着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.63,0:19:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是条垃圾短信啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的行李不能少带点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.39,0:20:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦 里面有重要的东西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.09,0:20:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那么多必要的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内衣啊 毛巾啊 药啊 还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.63,0:20:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.33,0:20:37.83,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}ココロが死ぬよ　自分のためないが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.33,0:20:37.83,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}心已不随己地死去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:40.66,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}引き金になるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:40.66,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}做抛砖引玉之用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:48.97,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}助かる君えと　信じて君からもれだ声に呼んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:48.97,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}被我所信任的 拯救我的你之声所呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.34,0:20:54.95,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}奇跡を　いもの追っか駆ける悲劇は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.34,0:20:54.95,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}那奇迹 那追逐虚像而去的悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:57.41,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}終わらないこと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:57.41,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}永无终止之日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:21:05.79,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}闇の奥で繰り返す叫び いとに痛み悪意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:21:05.79,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}在黑暗泥沼中不断的呐喊 及那深沉的恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.84,0:21:09.03,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}選ばれしだから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.84,0:21:09.03,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}这就是被选中的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:13.43,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}泣きたくない　これ以上愛たくない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:13.43,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}不愿再哭泣 再不愿去爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:17.30,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}燃える　愛しいさが通差した
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:17.30,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}燃烧的爱意却穿体而过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:21.53,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}愛きて　泣きたく追い駆けて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:21.53,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}抹掉泪水 去追逐那爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:25.66,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}誰にも　止められない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.55,0:21:25.66,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}谁都无法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.67,0:21:30.25,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}これは未来　それとも夢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.67,0:21:30.25,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}此乃未来 抑或是梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.27,0:21:33.57,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}答えは何処だろ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.27,0:21:33.57,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}答案不得而知
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.80,0:21:38.37,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}これが今を　試す扉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.80,0:21:38.37,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}若此为如今的试炼之门
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:41.66,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}壊すは開けれない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:41.66,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}毁灭也无法将其开启
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.67,0:21:44.74,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}どしよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.67,0:21:44.74,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\blur4}该如何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:51.68,fix,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HEC00C1&\move(665,31,545,31)}姆鲁姆鲁{\c&H5B6F5D&}老师的{\c&HFBF9F9&}秘密未来日记
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:51.68,fix,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz359.479\fs32\c&HE85239&\move(554,320,523,320)}4th{\c&HFCFCFC&}的{\c&H240BB9&}由来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:51.68,fix,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H073027&\fs35\c&HFDFAFC&\pos(616,479)}来须圭悟篇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.26,0:21:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}4/21 10:23 咖啡屋“隐居”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:22:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 你也被选为12位日记所有人之一了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.26,0:22:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是您的维也纳咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.61,0:22:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.12,0:22:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气 请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.90,0:22:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.97,0:22:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想要手办模型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢弹模型
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.96,0:22:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.75,0:22:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.28,0:22:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班上的家伙都说扎古比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.78,0:22:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是比较喜欢钢弹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.80,0:22:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比起钢弹更…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.84,0:22:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.26,0:22:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.69,0:22:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正这就是我成为警察的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.78,0:22:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我后来把它偷到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.46,0:22:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之的意思是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来被老爸发现狠K了一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.15,0:22:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就成了警察
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.92,0:22:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.46,0:22:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过当时老爸也干起了小偷的勾当
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.52,0:22:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个故事看来会很长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.00,0:22:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到工作的老爸人间蒸发
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.79,0:22:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后搞垮身体死在了路边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.52,0:23:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到现在也这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.73,0:23:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没人去揍老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.91,0:23:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.93,0:23:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是为了揍人才成为警察的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.11,0:23:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以这么说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.24,0:23:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜查日记
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.64,0:23:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就心怀感激地收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.38,0:23:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我自己一人也能揍得了人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香肠还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}于是姆鲁姆鲁把维也纳咖啡（Wiener Kaffee）想成香肠和咖啡两样了。日语中香肠也就是Wiener。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.84,0:23:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匿名设定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.84,0:23:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}匿名设定就是设置不让对方知道自己的电话号码。

